Structure of the SWITCH/SwissSign hierarchy

The end-entity certs are signed by the SWITCH-CA with hash c4435d12.
The namespace for end-entity certs is restectied to

"/C=CH/O=Berner Fachhochschule - Haute ecole specialisee bernoise/*"

and the static hierarchy:

SwissSign Root (7b2d086c)
 +-- SwissSign Bronze (e36e7a72)
      +-- SwissSign Silver (e9d08b40)
           +-- SWITCH CA (c4435d12)

-----
SwissSignRoot.pem
7b2d086c
subject= /C=CH/O=SwissSign/CN=SwissSign CA (RSA IK May 6 1999 18:00:58)/emailAddress=ca@SwissSign.com
issuer= /C=CH/O=SwissSign/CN=SwissSign CA (RSA IK May 6 1999 18:00:58)/emailAddress=ca@SwissSign.com
-----
SwissSign_Bronze_CA.pem
e36e7a72
subject= /CN=SwissSign Bronze CA/emailAddress=bronze@swisssign.com/O=SwissSign/C=CH
issuer= /C=CH/O=SwissSign/CN=SwissSign CA (RSA IK May 6 1999 18:00:58)/emailAddress=ca@SwissSign.com
-----
SwissSign_Silver_CA.pem
e9d08b40
subject= /CN=SwissSign Silver CA/emailAddress=silver@swisssign.com/O=SwissSign/C=CH
issuer= /CN=SwissSign Bronze CA/emailAddress=bronze@swisssign.com/O=SwissSign/C=CH
-----
SWITCH-CA.txt
c4435d12
subject= /CN=SWITCH CA/emailAddress=switch.ca@switch.ch/O=Switch - Teleinformatikdienste fuer Lehre und Forschung/C=CH
issuer= /CN=SwissSign Silver CA/emailAddress=silver@swisssign.com/O=SwissSign/C=CH



Organisation namespace
----------------------
Extract using
 awk  '/^O =/ { s=substr($0,5,length($0)-6); print "/C=CH/O="s"/*";} ' README
 
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Berner Fachhochschule - Haute ecole specialisee bernoise/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=ETH Swiss Federal Institute of Technology Zurich/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Fachhochschule Aargau Nordwestschweiz/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Fachhochschule beider Basel/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Kantonale Technikerinnen- und Techniker-Schule fuer Informatik/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=PSI - Paul Scherrer Institut/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=SWITCH - Teleinformatikdienste fuer Lehre und Forschung/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Universitaet Bern/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Universite de Fribourg - Universitaet Freiburg/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Universite de Geneve/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Universite de Lausanne/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Universitaet Luzern/*"'
 cond_subjects  globus  '"/C=CH/O=Universitaet Zuerich/*"'
